

d.measure - 

d.measure provides the user with an @glossary("interactive",16.glossary/interactve.def) way to measure the
lengths and areas of @glossary("lines",16.glossary/line.def) and @glossary("polygons",16.glossary/polygon.def) drawn by the user in the
active @glossary("frame",16.glossary/graphframe.def) on the graphics monitor.  Lines and polygons are drawn
using a pointing device (@glossary("mouse",16.glossary/mouse.def)).

